<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10109072>
    dc:description "FIGURE 28. A–G, Xanthogryllacris timoriensis (Karny, 1931): male (A–E), female (F–G); H–L, Prosopogryllacris gamta sp. nov. female holotype (H–K), not a type (L).—Habitus dorsal view (A, H) and lateral view (F), face (B, I), male abdominal apex in apical (C), dorsal (D) and lateral view (E), female abdominal apex with seventh abdominal sternite and subgenital plate in ventral (G, J) and lateral view (K), ovipositor (L). Scales 10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10109072/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

